{"tid":2344851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"豐澤樓污水樣本驗出病毒　或有患者連續多日使用洗手間","createTime":"2020-12-29T05:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T06:18:27.000Z","uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"99e806687fa10aba743204b5b8fb274c4f3f7034","tid":2344851,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"港大研究團隊在未有確診者的彩雲邨豐澤樓，4個污水樣本驗出新型冠狀病毒，豐澤樓居民須強制檢測。有份參與研究的港大公共衞生學院教授潘烈文表示，<span class=\"red\">豐澤樓情況不尋常，研究結果顯示，或有患者連續多日使用洗手間，好可能是大廈居民。</span><br />\n<br />\n潘烈文表示，今次的研究方法，需要從稀釋的污水中找出病毒，涉及大量時間和工序，難以在全港各座樓宇大量進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567601-20201229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567601-20201229.htm&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=323f9bbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567601-20201229.htm&h=e50cf9e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567601-20201229.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6600d566bd019d12ea9c39b6bd10e78b24765357","tid":2344851,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"豐澤：WTF? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df22c27a5f83643d4912b357cfea8aafcee6f3ca","tid":2344851,"uid":76063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"有邊個唔使日日去自己屋企廁所 on99"},{"pid":"9130eb73a444cdd156b2af17f7c20eadbe0e21ff","tid":2344851,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b9443200f705f96c56a111d9fabdf569021547","tid":2344851,"uid